  "texts": [
    "Table 5 shows all keywords in descending order according to their average normalized citations.",
    "The table also contains information on occurrence, average publication year, and average citation.",
    "The following is a summary of several important elements shown in Table 5: 1.",
    "Deep learning, machine learning, AI, and CC are the most popular keywords in the field of AI-in-CC-in-CI, showing that the use of these technologies in the CI is attracting more and more attention (Li et al., 2018; Li et al., 2020; Li et al., 2021; Shah et al., 2022).",
    "Aside from AI technology, the Internet of Things, blockchain, big data, and other cut-ting-edge technologies are also extensively used in the CI (You and Feng, 2020; Abunadi et al., 2022)."
  ]
}